</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_218" id="107v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_218_r3l1">München </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_218_r3l2"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnd / . Wır ſüllen auf den Mıtwochen in der <expan>Pfıngſtvvoch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r3l3">ſchirſt / cʒü Jngolſtat / vor <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> hercʒog Stephan / mit <expan>Hılpolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r3l4"><expan>Frawmberg<ex>er</ex></expan> einen tag ſüchen / . vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> eın </del> daʒ Jr vns einen ewrs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r3l5">Rats den Rıdler <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> Görgen Kacʒmeyr leıhen vnd <expan>ſchıcke<ex>n</ex></expan> vvollet / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r3l6">der auf den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> tag güt cʒeıt kum gen <expan>Jngolſt<ex>at</ex></expan> vnd do bey den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r3l7">ſeÿ / . Als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>frewntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> des <expan>ſünderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> vvol getrawen / Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r3l8">das in ſölıchen vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> vmb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> allcʒıt <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dıene<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r3l9">vvöllen / . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_218" id="107v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>München </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnd, wir süllen auf den <app><note><q type="date">mitwochen in der
                            <expan>pfingstwoch<ex>e</ex>n</expan></q>29.05.1409</note></app> schirst czü Ingolstat vor
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, herczog Stephan, mit
                                <expan>Hilpolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Frawmberg<ex>er</ex></expan> einen tag süchen. Und
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir uns einen ewrs rats, den
                        Ridler <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> Görgen Kaczmeyr, leihen und
                                <expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan> wollet, daz der auf den
                                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> tag güt czeit kum gen
                                <expan>Ingolst<ex>at</ex></expan> und do bey den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sey, als wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> des <expan>sünderl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        wol getrawen und das in sölichen und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> allczit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>diene<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllen. </ab>
</div>
